{"tid":1006824,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[ 大掃除 ] 失戀青年全屋物件掟落街","createTime":"2019-02-03T09:31:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-03T13:41:55.000Z","uid":215207,"like":461,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"87fb146cdf87624134d8dd33ea6ab53cce079923","tid":1006824,"uid":215207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T09:31:46.000Z","msg":"電視機　電腦　枱櫈　廚具　衣物&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n失戀青年全屋物件掟落街<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】天水圍天悅出現高空擲物狂徒，一名青年疑受失戀打擊精神大受刺激，昨日瘋狂地將屋內的家具、電器及雜物等掟落街中，警方接報封鎖現場，與擲物狂徒對峙期間，他仍不停拋下大小物件，最後屋內除重型電器及床外，幾乎全被他拋清光，幸而未有傷及途人。事件擾攘兩個多小時後，警方破門入屋將狂徒制服送院，他涉嫌高空擲物被扣查。　<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/640pix/20050328/Article_news/28la2p3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2F640pix%2F20050328%2FArticle_news%2F28la2p3.jpg&h=4dc2e11b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/640pix/20050327/Article_news/27la2p11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2F640pix%2F20050327%2FArticle_news%2F27la2p11.jpg&h=05aa471e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n青年疑失戀，不停將屋內電器及雜物擲落街上，警方將現場封鎖，地上滿布被擲下的家具及雜物。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/640pix/20050327/Article_news/27la2p133.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2F640pix%2F20050327%2FArticle_news%2F27la2p133.jpg&h=ec6ddf85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n青年所住單位事發後空空如也，只剩下幾件大型家具及電器。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/640pix/20050327/Article_news/27la2p16.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2F640pix%2F20050327%2FArticle_news%2F27la2p16.jpg&h=0f6f4e07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被男事主擲下的一張床褥，從三十六樓飛下街中。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/640pix/20050327/Article_news/27la2p14.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2F640pix%2F20050327%2FArticle_news%2F27la2p14.jpg&h=4d4a497a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n發狂擲物落街的男事主，不時在屋內大聲呼叫。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/640pix/20050327/Article_news/newx111.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2F640pix%2F20050327%2FArticle_news%2Fnewx111.gif&h=ce088699&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"747df0f36228bbc259e9184e01003d3004acd035","tid":1006824,"uid":215207,"like":58,"dislike":2,"score":56,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T09:32:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82cfc39042814123258d80a5d9b60cee0951939e","tid":1006824,"uid":65253,"like":108,"dislike":1,"score":107,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T09:33:45.000Z","msg":"大掃除"},{"pid":"0d5f0ddbc3b12b7ff1337595c685ff3d745df8cd","tid":1006824,"uid":99700,"like":193,"dislike":3,"score":190,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T09:34:54.000Z","msg":"床褥都伸到出個窗"},{"pid":"44b8f042fc456db7e8510c681e8da424dddaf908","tid":1006824,"uid":93986,"like":118,"dislike":2,"score":116,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T09:36:50.000Z","msg":"點解唔掉自己出去"},{"pid":"a8242d34da15f955d61159301b5b3d8f4701ec51","tid":1006824,"uid":215207,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"0d5f0ddbc3b12b7ff1337595c685ff3d745df8cd","tid":1006824,"uid":99700,"like":193,"dislike":3,"score":190,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T09:34:54.000Z","msg":"床褥都伸到出個窗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T09:36:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes1000.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes1000.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src